{"type":"message","id":"08c7c085","parentId":"d0617010","timestamp":"2026-05-28T02:07:14.092Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the commits with dates. Let me organize this nicely, grouping the meaningful ones and filtering out noise (merge commits, test/revert loops). The user asked for Feishu - I'll format it nicely for Feishu chat.\n\nLet me organize by day and highlight the important commits with their TAPD links as clickable URLs.\n\nActually, looking at the user's request more carefully - they want their commit logs from the past 7 days, with links made into hyperlinks. This is for display in Feishu chat. Let me create a clean, well-organized summary.\n\nI'll exclude:\n- Merge commits (just noise)\n- Test/revert loops (unless they're meaningful)\n\nAnd keep:\n- --story= tasks\n- --bug= fixes  \n- Feature commits\n- Optimization commits\n\nLet me organize by date with links converted to clickable URLs.\n\nFor Feishu, I can use markdown-like format: [text](url)\n\nLet me organize it nicely.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好嘞，整理好了！以下是最近 7 天你在 `nightoffullmoon` 的提交日志：\n\n---\n\n**📅 5/25（周一）**\n- `--story=1036439` 小汤联动皮肤 - 客户端 → [TAPD](https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1493650)\n- `--story=1038279` 小汤神话级英雄框常驻特效 → [TAPD](https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1493689)\n- `--story=1036439` 小汤联动皮肤 - 客户端（后面还有多次提交指向同一个需求）→ [TAPD](https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1494113)\n- 选中反转开关\n- 表数据更新 ×2\n\n**📅 5/26（周二）**\n- `--story=1036439` 小汤联动皮肤 - 客户端（多轮提交）→ [TAPD](https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1494113)\n- `--story=1036439` 次提交 → [TAPD](https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1495227)\n- 播放Timeline支持敌方翻转Y功能\n- 变身的时候层级调整\n- 打包优化\n- 代码优化 / 代码更新 / 数据更新\n\n**📅 5/27（周三）**\n- `--bug=1016758` 没有皮肤的英雄背景显示错误 → [TAPD](https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1495477)\n- `--bug=1016765` 普通英雄进入战斗后头像消失 → [TAPD](https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1495547)\n- `--story=1038703` 英雄皮肤语音替换 - 客户端 → [TAPD](https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1495554)\n