{"type":"message","id":"8464a019","parentId":"55332003","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:44:14.520Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人发了一个视频文件，是关于刚刚提的 bug \"战斗中的皮肤动画没有背景\" 的复现视频。他应该是想让我把这个视频作为附件加到刚才提的 bug 单上。\n\n先看看这个视频，确认一下内容，然后加到 bug 单上。\n\nBug ID 是 `1131253609001016805`，详情页 URL 是 `https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/bug/detail/1131253609001016805`\n\n我需要把视频上传到 bug 单作为附件。根据 SKILL.md 的说明，上传附件的正确流程是：\n1. 打开 bug 编辑页\n2. 点 `#upload-attachement`\n3. 用 `#file_input` 上传文件\n4. 等 6s\n5. 提交表单\n\n但我得先看看这个视频内容，确认一下。不过主人发了视频，我应该能直接看到。\n\n让我看看视频文件路径，然后把它作为附件加到 bug 里。\n\n看 SKILL.md 中关于附件上传的部分，在编辑页面上传后可以提交表单保存。\n\n让我先看看这个视频最后几帧，确认内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_tjwdUM1DGZetrMWaZoDF9949","name":"image","arguments":{"image":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\033673d511f35b9b52f8d783e45421aa---751e504b-76c9-4234-96f7-3adcc6ed0aec.mp4","prompt":"Describe what this video shows about the bug - what's happening on screen?"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6785,"output":383,"cacheRead":40832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48000,"cost":{"input":0.0009499,"output":0.00010724000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001143296,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002200436}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779939849218,"responseId":"c94bfbeb-5f09-4e5c-8640-45eb3bd0cefd"}}
