{"type":"message","id":"572b9aff","parentId":"190ab126","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:49:12.199Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the user wants to add the video to bug 1016781. This is a different bug than the one I created. The full TAPD bug ID format is `1131253609001016781`.\n\nBut the TAPD cookies are expired. I need to handle the login first. Let me try a different approach - let me use 叶枝君's cookies instead of 周以天's cookies. Wait, looking at the cookies file path again...\n\nActually, looking at the SKILL.md and MEMORY.md:\n- Cookies file: `workspace/tapd_cookies.json` (default, 周以天)\n- 叶枝君 cookies: `workspace/tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json`\n\nThe create_bug.mjs script uses `tapd_cookies.json`, and it worked earlier. Let me check if the yezhijun cookies are still valid.\n\nActually, the issue was that tapd_cookies.json (周以天) expired. Let me check the yezhijun cookie too. Or maybe I should just do the re-login flow.\n\nBut wait - the user is asking me to add the video to bug 1016781. This is a different bug. Let me try with yezhijun's cookies first, since the user is Yousan(叶枝君) himself.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，之前周以天的 TAPD cookie 过期了，我试试你的账号 cookie。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_SvsUIKDoRWKnyC66HnQU3978","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"const fs=require('fs');const f='tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json';console.log(f,'exists:',fs.existsSync(f))\"","timeout":5,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":71,"output":429,"cacheRead":59392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59892,"cost":{"input":0.000009940000000000001,"output":0.00012012000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001662976,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001793036}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779940147149,"responseId":"ad97017b-60da-44f9-a4cf-cc756902edc4"}}
