{"type":"message","id":"ebd9d2e5","parentId":"ecab0ac6","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:49:47.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both cookies expired. The login was successful at www.tapd.cn but when navigating to the edit page, it redirected to login again. This means the cookies work for the main page but not for the edit page.\n\nWait, the script logged \"Logged in!\" which means visiting www.tapd.cn didn't redirect. But when going to the edit URL, it redirected. This could mean:\n1. The edit page requires a specific permission/session that the main page doesn't\n2. The subdomain cookie issue\n\nLet me check what cookies are being saved. Maybe I need to look at the cookie file more carefully.\n\nActually, this is interesting - the main page loads fine but the edit page redirects. This might be a separate TAPD issue, or the cookies for the edit page path are different.\n\nLet me try a different approach - use the headed mode with the QR code approach since both cookies are dead. But I need to show the QR code to the user.\n\nActually, let me try a completely different approach. The bug 1016781 is a different bug. Since I can't get the edit page to work with expired cookies, let me:\n\n1. Open the QR code login page in headed mode\n2. Take a screenshot\n3. Send it to the user\n4. Ask them to scan it\n5. Then continue\n\nLet me do this properly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"两个账号的 cookie 都过期了。我打开 TAPD 扫码页，主人扫一下重新登录。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_XeOnSVUHeD0bDnnF7faq9632","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\temp_relogin_attach.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\nconst FULL_BUG_ID = '1131253609001016781';\nconst VIDEO_PATH = 'C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\media\\\\inbound\\\\033673d511f35b9b52f8d783e45421aa---751e504b-76c9-4234-96f7-3adcc6ed0aec.mp4';\n\n(async () => {\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false });\n  const page = await browser.newPage();\n  \n  await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/cloud_logins/login', { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 });\n  await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n  \n  console.log('Page URL:', page.url());\n  console.log('Title:', await page.title());\n  \n  // Save QR code screenshot\n  await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_qrcode.png'), fullPage: false });\n  console.log('QR code screenshot saved');\n  \n  // Wait for login\n  console.log('Waiting for QR scan...');\n  let loggedIn = false;\n  for (let i = 0; i < 180; i++) {\n    await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n    const url = page.url();\n    if (!url.includes('login') && !url.includes('cloud_logins')) {\n      loggedIn = true;\n      console.log('Login success! URL:', url);\n      break;\n    }\n  }\n  \n  if (!loggedIn) {\n    console.log('Login timeout');\n    await browser.close();\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n  \n  // Save cookies\n  const cookies = await page.context().cookies();\n  fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\n  console.log('Cookies saved');\n  \n  // Now go to edit page\n  const editUrl = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id=${FULL_BUG_ID}`;\n  console.log('Opening edit page...');\n  await page.goto(editUrl, { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 });\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n  console.log('Edit page URL:', page.url());\n  \n  // Upload\n  console.log('Uploading...');\n  const uploadBtn = page.locator('#upload-attachement');\n  if (await uploadBtn.count() > 0) {\n    await uploadBtn.first().click();\n    await page.waitForTimeout(1500);\n  }\n  \n  await page.locator('#file_input').first().setInputFiles(VIDEO_PATH);\n  console.log('File set, waiting 10s...');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(10000);\n  \n  // Submit\n  await page.locator('#save_return, #_view, #save_view').first().click();\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n  \n  console.log('Final URL:', page.url());\n  await browser.close();\n  console.log('SUCCESS');\n})().catch(e => { console.error('ERROR:', e.message || e); process.exit(1); });\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":198,"output":1157,"cacheRead":61952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63307,"cost":{"input":0.000027720000000000002,"output":0.00032396000000000004,"cacheRead":0.001734656,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0020863360000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779940178385,"responseId":"0c04b14c-8dcb-4a93-92cd-b5e98130816e"}}
