{"type":"message","id":"df037a50","parentId":"431d063c","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:52:02.587Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人问每天登录到底能不能保活。让我检查一下保活脚本的具体实现，看看为什么保活没有生效。\n\n实际情况：\n1. 周以天：今天凌晨（T03:47）保活脚本执行了，但发现 session 已过期，exit code 1，没有成功续期\n2. 叶枝君：上次保活是5月20日，之后就没再执行过\n\n所以有两个问题：\n1. 叶枝君的保活为什么没跑？\n2. 周以天的保活为什么续不上？\n\n让我检查 HEARTBEAT.md 和保活脚本的实现。\n\n先看看 heartbeat 里的配置，再看看保活脚本是怎么实现的。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_AvbXvIaAsvT7KQqKtjGr0002","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\heartbeat-state.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_kZj21kdh1Dy3PDvuoPAl8440","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"console.log(require('fs').readFileSync('scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs','utf8').slice(0,2000))\"","timeout":10,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2418,"output":320,"cacheRead":63872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66610,"cost":{"input":0.00033852000000000003,"output":0.00008960000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001788416,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002216536}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779940318423,"responseId":"13e324dd-bcda-461b-ae29-892e06ed32b9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3f6f89e","parentId":"df037a50","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:52:02.967Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_AvbXvIaAsvT7KQqKtjGr0002","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access 'C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\memory\\\\heartbeat-state.json'\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"read","error":"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access 'C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\heartbeat-state.json'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779940322967}}
{"type":"message","id":"41d21736","parentId":"d3f6f89e","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:52:02.967Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_kZj21kdh1Dy3PDvuoPAl8440","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// TAPD Keepalive Script (支持双账号)\n// 用法: node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs [zhouyitian|yezhijun]\n//   默认 zhouyitian（周以天）\n//   指定 yezhijun 则保活叶枝君的 cookie\n//\n// Exit codes:\n//   0 = success (cookies refreshed)\n//   1 = cookie invalid / login expired (need re-login)\n//   2 = script error (network, etc.)\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\n\n// 账号参数\nconst ACCOUNT = process.argv[2] || 'zhouyitian';\nconst LABELS = { zhouyitian: '周以天', yezhijun: '叶枝君' };\nconst label = LABELS[ACCOUNT] || ACCOUNT;\n\nconst COOKIES_FILE = ACCOUNT === 'yezhijun'\n  ? path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json')\n  : path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json');\nconst STORAGE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, `tapd_storage_${ACCOUNT}.json`);\nconst STATE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', `tapd-keepalive-state-${ACCOUNT}.json`);\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function () {}, csi: function () {}, app: {} };\n};\n\nfunction log(msg) {\n  console.log(`[${new Date().toISOString()}] ${msg}`);\n}\n\nfunction writeState(state) {\n  try {\n    fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(STATE_FILE), { recursive: true });\n    fs.writeFileSync(STATE_FILE, JSON.stringify(state, null, 2));\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.error('Failed to write state:', e.message);\n  }\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(COOKIES_FILE)) {\n    log(`[${label}] ERROR: cookies file not found: ${COOKIES_FILE}`);\n    writeStat"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":342,"aggregated":"// TAPD Keepalive Script (支持双账号)\n// 用法: node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs [zhouyitian|yezhijun]\n//   默认 zhouyitian（周以天）\n//   指定 yezhijun 则保活叶枝君的 cookie\n//\n// Exit codes:\n//   0 = success (cookies refreshed)\n//   1 = cookie invalid / login expired (need re-login)\n//   2 = script error (network, etc.)\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\n\n// 账号参数\nconst ACCOUNT = process.argv[2] || 'zhouyitian';\nconst LABELS = { zhouyitian: '周以天', yezhijun: '叶枝君' };\nconst label = LABELS[ACCOUNT] || ACCOUNT;\n\nconst COOKIES_FILE = ACCOUNT === 'yezhijun'\n  ? path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json')\n  : path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json');\nconst STORAGE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, `tapd_storage_${ACCOUNT}.json`);\nconst STATE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', `tapd-keepalive-state-${ACCOUNT}.json`);\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function () {}, csi: function () {}, app: {} };\n};\n\nfunction log(msg) {\n  console.log(`[${new Date().toISOString()}] ${msg}`);\n}\n\nfunction writeState(state) {\n  try {\n    fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(STATE_FILE), { recursive: true });\n    fs.writeFileSync(STATE_FILE, JSON.stringify(state, null, 2));\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.error('Failed to write state:', e.message);\n  }\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(COOKIES_FILE)) {\n    log(`[${label}] ERROR: cookies file not found: ${COOKIES_FILE}`);\n    writeStat","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779940322967}}
{"type":"message","id":"fb92825a","parentId":"41d21736","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:52:05.753Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me see more of the keepalive script to understand why it fails.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Y7C9pcSb0842rm13cwFn9740","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"console.log(require('fs').readFileSync('scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs','utf8'))\"","timeout":10,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":25846,"output":136,"cacheRead":41344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67326,"cost":{"input":0.00361844,"output":0.00003808,"cacheRead":0.001157632,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004814152}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779940322969,"responseId":"3c4e2d15-e6ec-4539-875b-5deb7449b39d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"aa39dff9","parentId":"fb92825a","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:52:06.017Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Y7C9pcSb0842rm13cwFn9740","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// TAPD Keepalive Script (支持双账号)\n// 用法: node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs [zhouyitian|yezhijun]\n//   默认 zhouyitian（周以天）\n//   指定 yezhijun 则保活叶枝君的 cookie\n//\n// Exit codes:\n//   0 = success (cookies refreshed)\n//   1 = cookie invalid / login expired (need re-login)\n//   2 = script error (network, etc.)\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\n\n// 账号参数\nconst ACCOUNT = process.argv[2] || 'zhouyitian';\nconst LABELS = { zhouyitian: '周以天', yezhijun: '叶枝君' };\nconst label = LABELS[ACCOUNT] || ACCOUNT;\n\nconst COOKIES_FILE = ACCOUNT === 'yezhijun'\n  ? path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json')\n  : path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json');\nconst STORAGE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, `tapd_storage_${ACCOUNT}.json`);\nconst STATE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', `tapd-keepalive-state-${ACCOUNT}.json`);\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function () {}, csi: function () {}, app: {} };\n};\n\nfunction log(msg) {\n  console.log(`[${new Date().toISOString()}] ${msg}`);\n}\n\nfunction writeState(state) {\n  try {\n    fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(STATE_FILE), { recursive: true });\n    fs.writeFileSync(STATE_FILE, JSON.stringify(state, null, 2));\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.error('Failed to write state:', e.message);\n  }\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(COOKIES_FILE)) {\n    log(`[${label}] ERROR: cookies file not found: ${COOKIES_FILE}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: 'cookies_missing', at: new Date().toISOString(), account: ACCOUNT });\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n\n  const oldCookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  log(`[${label}] Loaded ${oldCookies.length} cookies`);\n\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless: true,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'],\n  });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 },\n    userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/125.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n  });\n  await ctx.addCookies(oldCookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.addInitScript(STEALTH_INIT);\n\n  try {\n    log(`[${label}] Visiting workspace dashboard...`);\n    const resp = await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n    const url = page.url();\n    const title = await page.title();\n    const status = resp?.status();\n    log(`[${label}] HTTP ${status} | url=${url} | title=${title}`);\n\n    if (url.includes('login') || title.includes('登录') || title.includes('WAF')) {\n      log(`[${label}] Session EXPIRED - need re-login`);\n      writeState({\n        ok: false,\n        error: 'session_expired',\n        at: new Date().toISOString(),\n        finalUrl: url,\n        title,\n        account: ACCOUNT,\n      });\n      await browser.close();\n      process.exit(1);\n    }\n\n    // Bonus: also poke the main page to make sure session stays active\n    await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/story/list', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    }).catch(() => {});\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n    // Save refreshed cookies\n    const newCookies = await ctx.cookies();\n    const newStorage = await ctx.storageState();\n\n    // 同时更新主文件（如果是周以天）和备份文件\n    fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(newCookies, null, 2));\n    if (ACCOUNT === 'zhouyitian') {\n      // 主 tapd_cookies.json 也保持为周以天（提单用）\n      fs.writeFileSync(path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json'), JSON.stringify(newCookies, null, 2));\n    }\n    fs.writeFileSync(STORAGE_FILE, JSON.stringify(newStorage, null, 2));\n\n    const tapdsession = newCookies.find((c) => c.name === 'tapdsession');\n    const exp = tapdsession?.expires > 0\n      ? new Date(tapdsession.expires * 1000).toISOString()\n      : 'session';\n\n    log(`[${label}] Refreshed ${newCookies.length} cookies | tapdsession exp: ${exp}`);\n    writeState({\n      ok: true,\n      at: new Date().toISOString(),\n      cookieCount: newCookies.length,\n      tapdsessionExpires: exp,\n      title,\n      account: ACCOUNT,\n    });\n\n    await browser.close();\n    process.exit(0);\n  } catch (e) {\n    log(`[${label}] ERROR: ${e.message}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: e.message, at: new Date().toISOString(), account: ACCOUNT });\n    try { await browser.close(); } catch {}\n    process.exit(2);\n  }\n}\n\nmain();"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":242,"aggregated":"// TAPD Keepalive Script (支持双账号)\n// 用法: node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs [zhouyitian|yezhijun]\n//   默认 zhouyitian（周以天）\n//   指定 yezhijun 则保活叶枝君的 cookie\n//\n// Exit codes:\n//   0 = success (cookies refreshed)\n//   1 = cookie invalid / login expired (need re-login)\n//   2 = script error (network, etc.)\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\n\n// 账号参数\nconst ACCOUNT = process.argv[2] || 'zhouyitian';\nconst LABELS = { zhouyitian: '周以天', yezhijun: '叶枝君' };\nconst label = LABELS[ACCOUNT] || ACCOUNT;\n\nconst COOKIES_FILE = ACCOUNT === 'yezhijun'\n  ? path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json')\n  : path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json');\nconst STORAGE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, `tapd_storage_${ACCOUNT}.json`);\nconst STATE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', `tapd-keepalive-state-${ACCOUNT}.json`);\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function () {}, csi: function () {}, app: {} };\n};\n\nfunction log(msg) {\n  console.log(`[${new Date().toISOString()}] ${msg}`);\n}\n\nfunction writeState(state) {\n  try {\n    fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(STATE_FILE), { recursive: true });\n    fs.writeFileSync(STATE_FILE, JSON.stringify(state, null, 2));\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.error('Failed to write state:', e.message);\n  }\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(COOKIES_FILE)) {\n    log(`[${label}] ERROR: cookies file not found: ${COOKIES_FILE}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: 'cookies_missing', at: new Date().toISOString(), account: ACCOUNT });\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n\n  const oldCookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  log(`[${label}] Loaded ${oldCookies.length} cookies`);\n\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless: true,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'],\n  });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 },\n    userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/125.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n  });\n  await ctx.addCookies(oldCookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.addInitScript(STEALTH_INIT);\n\n  try {\n    log(`[${label}] Visiting workspace dashboard...`);\n    const resp = await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n    const url = page.url();\n    const title = await page.title();\n    const status = resp?.status();\n    log(`[${label}] HTTP ${status} | url=${url} | title=${title}`);\n\n    if (url.includes('login') || title.includes('登录') || title.includes('WAF')) {\n      log(`[${label}] Session EXPIRED - need re-login`);\n      writeState({\n        ok: false,\n        error: 'session_expired',\n        at: new Date().toISOString(),\n        finalUrl: url,\n        title,\n        account: ACCOUNT,\n      });\n      await browser.close();\n      process.exit(1);\n    }\n\n    // Bonus: also poke the main page to make sure session stays active\n    await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/story/list', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    }).catch(() => {});\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n    // Save refreshed cookies\n    const newCookies = await ctx.cookies();\n    const newStorage = await ctx.storageState();\n\n    // 同时更新主文件（如果是周以天）和备份文件\n    fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(newCookies, null, 2));\n    if (ACCOUNT === 'zhouyitian') {\n      // 主 tapd_cookies.json 也保持为周以天（提单用）\n      fs.writeFileSync(path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json'), JSON.stringify(newCookies, null, 2));\n    }\n    fs.writeFileSync(STORAGE_FILE, JSON.stringify(newStorage, null, 2));\n\n    const tapdsession = newCookies.find((c) => c.name === 'tapdsession');\n    const exp = tapdsession?.expires > 0\n      ? new Date(tapdsession.expires * 1000).toISOString()\n      : 'session';\n\n    log(`[${label}] Refreshed ${newCookies.length} cookies | tapdsession exp: ${exp}`);\n    writeState({\n      ok: true,\n      at: new Date().toISOString(),\n      cookieCount: newCookies.length,\n      tapdsessionExpires: exp,\n      title,\n      account: ACCOUNT,\n    });\n\n    await browser.close();\n    process.exit(0);\n  } catch (e) {\n    log(`[${label}] ERROR: ${e.message}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: e.message, at: new Date().toISOString(), account: ACCOUNT });\n    try { await browser.close(); } catch {}\n    process.exit(2);\n  }\n}\n\nmain();","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779940326017}}
{"type":"message","id":"9bb42f63","parentId":"aa39dff9","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:52:15.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture. The keepalive script works by visiting `www.tapd.cn/31253609/` and then `tapd_fe.tapd.cn`. When the cookies are valid, TAPD's server extends the session automatically (tapdsession gets a new 7-day expiry).\n\nThe issue is:\n1. **叶枝君** - Last keepalive was 5月20日. After that, the session expired on 5月27日. Since no keepalive ran between 5/20 and 5/28 (today), the session died. Looking at HEARTBEAT.md, both accounts should be checked daily. The heartbeat must not have been running or the state check didn't trigger the keepalive.\n\n2. **周以天** - The keepalive ran today at 03:47, but it found the session expired (exit code 1). This means the previous keepalive didn't run often enough, or the session expired between runs.\n\nSo the real question is: can the keepalive actually prevent expiry? The answer is **yes, theoretically** - visiting TAPD should extend the `tapdsession` cookie by 7 days. But it only works if it runs regularly (every day or two) while the cookie is still valid.\n\nThe failure modes:\n- If the heartbeat doesn't run (e.g., no new messages trigger it), the keepalive doesn't execute\n- If the session already expired before the keepalive script runs, it can't self-heal (that would require re-login)\n\nFor 周以天, the keepalive ran at 03:47 today and found the session expired. This means the previous keepalive didn't run for more than 7 days, or the session expired earlier for some other reason.\n\nFor 叶枝君, the keepalive hasn't run since 5月20日.\n\nLet me explain this to the owner. The keepalive mechanism works **only if it runs while the session is still valid**. Once it's expired, you need a manual re-login. The problem is that the heartbeat might not be triggering often enough, or the keepalive script hasn't been consistently running.\n\nLet me suggest a fix - maybe I should add a cron job instead of relying on heartbeat, since heartbeat only runs when there's activity.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"保活逻辑本身没问题——每天访问一次 TAPD 页面，服务器会自动续 `tapdsession` 7 天。\n\n问题出在两个地方：\n\n**1. 叶枝君的保活上次跑是 5月20日，之后再也没跑过**\n保活是靠 HEARTBEAT 触发的，但 heartbeat 只在有消息进来时才运行。如果那段时间没人跟我说话，heartbeat 就没触发，保活就断了。\n\n**2. 周以天今天凌晨跑了一次，但发现 session 已经过期了**\n说明上次保活到这次之间间隔超过 7 天，中间断了。\n\n根本原因：**heartbeat 不是定时器**，它依赖于有人发消息。没人说话就不触发，保活就跳过了。\n\n建议改成 **cron 定时任务**，每天固定时间跑，不受消息流影响。要我加一个吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1651,"output":679,"cacheRead":67200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69530,"cost":{"input":0.00023114,"output":0.00019012,"cacheRead":0.0018816,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00230286}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779940326019,"responseId":"68cddb3e-e4ff-46db-ad70-2c27bc9019e8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"eafe190a","parentId":"9bb42f63","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:53:53.150Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6e4f8ab6a480b3eb32d79c988b3]\nYousan(叶枝君): 加一个, 这样cookie就能永远存活吗"}],"timestamp":1779940433143}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e4f8ab6a480b3eb32d79c988b3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-05-28 11:53 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"ce2e1e98","parentId":"eafe190a","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:53:53.152Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"087a8084","parentId":"ce2e1e98","timestamp":"2026-05-28T03:54:00.910Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人问：\n1. 加 cron 定时任务\n2. 这样 cookie 就能永远存活吗？\n\n关于第二个问题：TAPD 的 `tapdsession` cookie 每次访问页面会续期 7 天。理论上只要每天跑一次保活，session 就永远过期不了。但有几个潜在问题：\n- TAPD 服务器端可能会有 session 上限时间（比如有些系统即使你一直续，也会强制 30 天重新登录）\n- 如果保活脚本因为网络问题、TAPD 改版、WAF 拦截等原因失败，就会中断\n- 所以不能保证「永远」，但可以做到只要脚本正常运行就持续存活\n\n我应该诚实回答这个问题。\n\n现在先解决：\n1. 主人还在等着扫码登录上传附件呢\n2. 先问主人扫码了没，先把附件上传完\n3. 然后再加 cron\n\n不过等一下，扫码登录的浏览器还在 background 跑着（session quick-reef）。主人可能还没扫码。我先回答他的问题。\n\n让我先看看怎么加 cron。OpenClaw 的 cron 配置方式需要查文档。\n\nActually, let me check the docs/cron 相关的内容。\n\n不过先回复主人吧——告诉他理论上是可行的，只要每天成功访问一次页面续期就不会断，但也有极端情况（TAPD 服务器强制要求重新登录）。然后先处理当前的事——扫码上传附件，再加 cron。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"理论上是这样的：`tapdsession` 每次访问页面会续 7 天，只要 cron 每天跑一次，就不应该过期。\n\n但有几个潜在风险：\n1. TAPD 可能做**安全策略升级**，强制周期重登（目前没发现）\n2. **保活脚本本身出问题**（WAF拦截、网络波动等）导致续期失败\n3. **密码被重置或账号被踢**等极端情况\n\n总的来说，只要脚本稳定运行，**可以做到持续存活不出问题**。\n\n我先加上 cron，然后处理眼前的事——你扫刚才那个码了吗？扫了我先传附件。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4048,"output":436,"cacheRead":65536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70020,"cost":{"input":0.00056672,"output":0.00012208,"cacheRead":0.001835008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0025238079999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779940433152,"responseId":"dcbd1997-f122-4482-850f-e8dd8250b248"}}
