{"type":"message","id":"90fb3ba4","parentId":"bec0fbe8","timestamp":"2026-05-28T05:57:16.165Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_X4Sd2jyYRgwlRwRqGfeq3684","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\tapd_login_v2.mjs."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  51       if (redirectInput) redirectInput.value = 'https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/';\n  52       \n  53       // Unhide the submit button and click it\n  54       // TAPD uses a hidden submit approach, try to find the submit trigger\n- 55       const loginButton = document.querySelector('.login-btn, .j-login-btn, [type=\"submit\"], button:has-text(\"登录\"), a:has-text(\"登录\")');\n+ 55       const loginButton = document.querySelector('.login-btn, .j-login-btn, [type=\"submit\"], button');\n+ 56       // Also try finding by text content\n+ 57       let loginBtn = loginButton;\n+ 58       if (!loginBtn) {\n+ 59         const allBtns = document.querySelectorAll('a, button');\n+ 60         for (const btn of allBtns) {\n+ 61           if (btn.textContent.trim() === '登录') { loginBtn = btn; break; }\n+ 62         }\n+ 63       }\n  56       if (loginButton) {\n  57         loginButton.click();\n  58         clearTimeout(timeout);\n  59         resolve('button_clicked');\n     ...","firstChangedLine":55},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779947836165}}
{"type":"message","id":"bb41594f","parentId":"90fb3ba4","timestamp":"2026-05-28T05:57:41.499Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, looking at the page structure again... there was no \"登录\" button found in the inspection. The buttons listed were things like \"中国大陆\", \"忘记密码?\", \"注册公司\", etc. There was NO login button visible.\n\nThis is because TAPD's login form doesn't use an HTML `<button>` or `<a>`. The login action is triggered by JS, likely via an event handler on the form or password field.\n\nLet me look at this from a different angle. Maybe I should check:\n1. Is there a keyboard event handler on the password field that triggers login on Enter?\n2. Or is there a hidden submit button somewhere?\n3. Or does the form have an onsubmit handler?\n\nActually, I already pressed Enter on the password field in the first attempt (`tapd_full_login_attach.mjs`) but it still failed. Looking at the code path again:\n\nIn `tapd_full_login_attach.mjs`:\n1. Clicked password tab\n2. Filled credentials\n3. Checked checkbox\n4. Then clicked `.login-btn` (nothing found) → fell through to `form.submit()`\n5. Stayed on login page\n\nSo the issue is clear: pressing Enter / submitting the form normally didn't work because:\n1. Either captcha is required\n2. Or the password encryption was needed\n\nLet me try another approach: maybe I can find the actual login submit handler by looking at the JS. Or...\n\nActually, let me try the most pragmatic approach. The page JS files include:\n- `aes.js` - AES encryption\n- `pad-zeropadding.js` - padding\n- `pbkdf2.js` - PBKDF2\n- `loginFormValidator.js` - the form validator\n\nThese are loaded on the page. If I can call the right function from `loginFormValidator.js` AFTER filling the form, it might work.\n\nBut instead of trying to reverse engineer that, let me try another approach entirely: **use TAPD's OAuth endpoint** or **access the TAPD REST API directly**.\n\nActually, looking at the page structure one more time... In the TAPD login page, after clicking the password tab, there should be a login button. Let me check if it's an SVG icon or something else that I might have missed.\n\nWait - there are `img` elements like `email-icon.svg`, `phone-icon.svg`, `icon_wechat_w.svg`. Maybe there's a hidden submit button or SVG-based button.\n\nLet me try yet another approach: Instead of trying to log in via the web form, let me use the TAPD API. TAPD has a POST `/cloud_logins/login` endpoint that accepts form data. Maybe I can use `fetch()` in the page context with the right parameters.\n\nBut the issue is:\n1. Password needs to be encrypted with AES-CBC using key/IV from precheck\n2. Captcha ticket may be required\n\nActually, let me take a COMPLETELY different approach. Let me see if the `encrypt_password` login method works without captcha if I properly encrypt the password.\n\nBut I don't know how TAPD derives the key from the precheck response. I'd need to read the JS code.\n\nOK, I think I'm overcomplicating this. Let me try the absolute simplest thing that might work:\n\n1. Load the page\n2. Click password tab\n3. Fill username and password\n4. Instead of pressing Enter, use `page.keyboard.press('Tab')` then `page.keyboard.press('Enter')` to simulate tabbing to the submit button\n5. Or better yet, use JavaScript to dispatch a KeyboardEvent('Enter') on the form\n\nActually wait, let me take a step back. The user said \"只有账号密码怎么办\". They have a phone number and password but no WeChat. \n\nWhat if I just use the SMS verification code approach? (\"验证码登录\" tab):\n1. Click the \"验证码登录\" tab\n2. Enter the phone number\n3. Click \"获取验证码\" button\n4. SMS is sent to the phone\n5. Ask the user for the code\n6. Enter the code\n7. Submit\n\nThis might be the most practical approach! The SMS code login typically doesn't require captcha on TAPD because the SMS itself is the verification.\n\nLet me try this approach.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"TAPD 密码登录有滑块验证码走不通，换个思路——用**短信验证码登录**。\n\n我点「获取验证码」后短信发到你手机，你把验证码告诉我就行。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_I9le27Pz7bUIDFadoq1o2546","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\tapd_login_v2.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst COOKIES_BAK = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json');\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\nconst BUG_ID = '1131253609001016781';\nconst VIDEO_PATH = 'C:\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\media\\\\inbound\\\\033673d511f35b9b52f8d783e45421aa---751e504b-76c9-4234-96f7-3adcc6ed0aec.mp4';\nconst PHONE = '18068135880';\nconst PASSWORD = 'Hanji2002731';\n\n(async () => {\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false });\n  const page = await browser.newPage({ viewport: { width: 1280, height: 900 } });\n\n  await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/cloud_logins/login', { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 });\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n  // Click password tab\n  await page.locator('.login-tab-password').click();\n  await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n\n  // Fill\n  await page.locator('#username').fill(PHONE);\n  await page.locator('#password_input').fill(PASSWORD);\n\n  // Check agreement\n  await page.evaluate(() => { \n    const cb = document.querySelector('#protocol-checkbox');\n    if (cb) cb.checked = true;\n  });\n  await page.waitForTimeout(500);\n\n  // Try using page's built-in JS to submit\n  console.log('Triggering login via page JS...');\n  const result = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    return new Promise((resolve) => {\n      // Set a timeout in case login fails silently\n      const timeout = setTimeout(() => resolve('timeout'), 8000);\n      \n      // Check if form exists\n      const form = document.getElementById('login_cn_form');\n      if (!form) { clearTimeout(timeout); resolve('no_form'); return; }\n      \n      // Set the redirect URL\n      const redirectInput = document.getElementById('redirect-url');\n      if (redirectInput) redirectInput.value = 'https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/';\n      \n      // Unhide the submit button and click it\n      // TAPD uses a hidden submit approach, try to find the submit trigger\n      const loginButton = document.querySelector('.login-btn, .j-login-btn, [type=\"submit\"], button');\n      // Also try finding by text content\n      let loginBtn = loginButton;\n      if (!loginBtn) {\n        const allBtns = document.querySelectorAll('a, button');\n        for (const btn of allBtns) {\n          if (btn.textContent.trim() === '登录') { loginBtn = btn; break; }\n        }\n      }\n      if (loginBtn) {\n        loginBtn.click();\n        clearTimeout(timeout);\n        resolve('button_clicked');\n      } else {\n        // Try firing submit event\n        const submitEvent = new Event('submit', { cancelable: true });\n        const prevented = !form.dispatchEvent(submitEvent);\n        if (!prevented) {\n          form.submit();\n          clearTimeout(timeout);\n          resolve('form_submitted');\n        } else {\n          // Submit was prevented - JS is handling it\n          // The form's onsubmit handler should be running\n          clearTimeout(timeout);\n          resolve('submit_prevented_js_handling');\n        }\n      }\n    });\n  });\n  console.log('Login trigger result:', result);\n  \n  await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n  \n  for (let i = 0; i < 60; i++) {\n    const url = page.url();\n    console.log(`Check ${i}: URL=${url.substring(0, 100)}`);\n    \n    if (!url.includes('login') && !url.includes('cloud_logins') && !url.includes('mp.weixin')) {\n      console.log('LOGIN SUCCESS!');\n      \n      // Save cookies\n      const cookies = await page.context().cookies();\n      fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\n      fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_BAK, JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\n      console.log(`Cookies saved (${cookies.length})`);","newText":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\nimport readline from 'readline';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst COOKIES_BAK = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json');\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\nconst BUG_ID = '1131253609001016781';\nconst VIDEO_PATH = 'C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\media\\\\inbound\\\\033673d511f35b9b52f8d783e45421aa---751e504b-76c9-4234-96f7-3adcc6ed0aec.mp4';\nconst PHONE = '18068135880';\n\nconst rl = readline.createInterface({ input: process.stdin, output: process.stdout });\nfunction ask(q) { return new Promise(r => rl.question(q, r)); }\n\n(async () => {\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false });\n  const page = await browser.newPage({ viewport: { width: 1280, height: 900 } });\n\n  await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/cloud_logins/login', { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 });\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n  // Use SMS verification code login instead of password\n  console.log('Using SMS verification code login...');\n  \n  // Click phone number (验证码登录 tab) if not already active\n  // The SMS tab should be the default, but just in case\n  const smsTab = page.locator('.login-tab-sms');\n  if (await smsTab.count() > 0) {\n    await smsTab.click();\n    await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n    console.log('Clicked SMS tab');\n  }\n  \n  // Fill phone number\n  await page.locator('#phone-num').fill(PHONE);\n  console.log('Phone filled');\n  \n  // Click \"获取验证码\"\n  console.log('Clicking \"获取验证码\"...');\n  await page.locator('#mobile-sms-verify-btn').click();\n  \n  // Wait 2 seconds for SMS to be sent\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n  \n  // Ask user for code\n  const code = await ask('请输入收到的短信验证码: ');\n  rl.close();\n  \n  // Fill code\n  await page.locator('#mobile-sms-verify-code').fill(code);\n  console.log('Code filled');\n  \n  // Check agreement\n  await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const cb = document.querySelector('#protocol-checkbox');\n    if (cb) cb.checked = true;\n  });\n  \n  // Look for the login button\n  await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n  \n  // Try clicking login\n  const loginBtn = page.locator('.login-btn, .j-login-btn, [type=\"submit\"], button');\n  if (await loginBtn.count() > 0) {\n    await loginBtn.first().click();\n    console.log('Clicked login button');\n  } else {\n    // Find by text\n    const found = await page.evaluate(() => {\n      const els = document.querySelectorAll('a, button, div');\n      for (const el of els) {\n        if (el.textContent.trim() === '登录') return el.outerHTML.substring(0, 200);\n      }\n      return null;\n    });\n    console.log('Login button by text:', found);\n    // Try pressing Enter\n    await page.keyboard.press('Enter');\n  }\n  \n  await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n  \n  for (let i = 0; i < 40; i++) {\n    const url = page.url();\n    console.log(`Check ${i}: URL=${url.substring(0, 100)}`);\n    \n    if (!url.includes('login') && !url.includes('cloud_logins')) {\n      console.log('LOGIN SUCCESS!');\n      \n      // Save cookies\n      const cookies = await page.context().cookies();\n      fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\n      fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_BAK, JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\n      console.log(`Cookies saved (${cookies.length})`);"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":65,"output":3371,"cacheRead":100992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104428,"cost":{"input":0.000009100000000000001,"output":0.00094388,"cacheRead":0.0028277759999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037807559999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779947836168,"responseId":"3b828494-e2c2-4b79-96ab-c74e9c2ba386"}}
