{"type":"message","id":"eb2688f1","parentId":"6fe0c816","timestamp":"2026-05-28T05:58:14.965Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is getting complicated. Let me take a completely different and much simpler approach.\n\nInstead of keeping the browser alive, let me just:\n1. Run a script that opens the login page, enters the phone, clicks \"获取验证码\", and then keeps the browser open\n2. Ask the user for the code\n3. When they reply, write the code to a file\n4. Run another script that continues from the same browser session\n\nActually, the simplest approach: Let me just ask the user to send me the code, then I'll enter it and continue.\n\nLet me simplify this a lot. I'll run a script that:\n1. Opens headed browser\n2. Clicks SMS tab, enters phone\n3. Clicks 获取验证码\n4. Keeps the session info in a file\n5. Waits for user input from a file\n\nThen:\n- I ask user → user replies with code\n- I write code to file\n- Script reads it and continues\n\nActually this is too complex. Let me just use a simpler approach - run the first part, then use a second script to reconnect to the same browser using `connectOverCDP`.\n\nHmm, but that requires the browser to be launched with `--remote-debugging-port`.\n\nOK let me just do it the simplest way possible:\n1. Run script that sends SMS and keeps browser alive for 120 seconds\n2. Ask user for code\n3. When user replies, quickly write a new script that reconnects, enters code, and continues\n\nActually no. Let me just try the simplest thing: run the step1 script (sends SMS + keeps browser alive), ask user, and when they reply I'll write the code to a JSON file that the waiting script can poll for.\n\nLet me write this properly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Va3pCtumanCZ3PLD99EA8796","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\tapd_login_with_code.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst COOKIES_BAK = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json');\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\nconst BUG_ID = '1131253609001016781';\nconst VIDEO_PATH = 'C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\media\\\\inbound\\\\033673d511f35b9b52f8d783e45421aa---751e504b-76c9-4234-96f7-3adcc6ed0aec.mp4';\nconst PHONE = '18068135880';\nconst WAIT_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, '_sms_code.json');\n\n(async () => {\n  // Clean up wait file\n  try { fs.unlinkSync(WAIT_FILE); } catch {}\n\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false });\n  const page = await browser.newPage({ viewport: { width: 1280, height: 900 } });\n\n  await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/cloud_logins/login', { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 });\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n  // SMS tab (should be default)\n  const smsTab = page.locator('.login-tab-sms');\n  if (await smsTab.count() > 0) {\n    await smsTab.click();\n    await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n  }\n\n  // Fill phone\n  await page.locator('#phone-num').fill(PHONE);\n  console.log('Phone filled');\n\n  // Click 获取验证码\n  console.log('Clicking 获取验证码...');\n  await page.locator('#mobile-sms-verify-btn').click();\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n  console.log('SMS sent!');\n\n  // Signal that we're waiting for the code\n  fs.writeFileSync(WAIT_FILE, JSON.stringify({ waiting: true }));\n\n  // Poll for the code file to be written\n  let code = null;\n  for (let i = 0; i < 180; i++) {\n    try {\n      const data = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(WAIT_FILE, 'utf8'));\n      if (data.code) {\n        code = data.code;\n        break;\n      }\n    } catch {}\n    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1000));\n  }\n\n  if (!code) {\n    console.log('Timeout waiting for SMS code');\n    await browser.close();\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n\n  console.log('Code received:', code);\n\n  // Fill code\n  await page.locator('#mobile-sms-verify-code').fill(code);\n  console.log('Code filled');\n\n  // Check agreement\n  await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const cb = document.querySelector('#protocol-checkbox');\n    if (cb) cb.checked = true;\n  });\n  await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n\n  // Find and click login button\n  await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const els = document.querySelectorAll('a, button, div, span, input');\n    for (const el of els) {\n      if (el.textContent?.trim() === '登录') {\n        if (el.tagName === 'A' || el.tagName === 'BUTTON' || el.tagName === 'INPUT' || el.tagName === 'DIV') {\n          el.click();\n          return;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  });\n\n  // Wait for redirect\n  for (let i = 0; i < 40; i++) {\n    const url = page.url();\n    console.log(`Check ${i}: ${url.substring(0, 100)}`);\n\n    if (!url.includes('login') && !url.includes('cloud_logins')) {\n      console.log('LOGIN SUCCESS!');\n\n      // Save cookies\n      const cookies = await page.context().cookies();\n      fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\n      fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_BAK, JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\n      console.log(`Cookies saved (${cookies.length})`);\n\n      // Upload attachment\n      const editUrl = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id=${BUG_ID}`;\n      console.log('Opening bug edit page...');\n      await page.goto(editUrl, { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 });\n      await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n      console.log('Edit page:', page.url());\n\n      if (!page.url().includes('login')) {\n        console.log('Uploading video...');\n        const uploadBtn = page.locator('#upload-attachement');\n        if (await uploadBtn.count() > 0) {\n          await uploadBtn.first().click();\n          await page.waitForTimeout(1500);\n        }\n        await page.locator('#file_input').first().setInputFiles(VIDEO_PATH);\n        console.log('File set, waiting 10s...');\n        await page.waitForTimeout(10000);\n\n        const saveBtn = page.locator('#save_return, #_view, #save_view');\n        if (await saveBtn.count() > 0) {\n          await saveBtn.first().click();\n        } else {\n          await page.evaluate(() => document.getElementById('bug_form')?.submit());\n        }\n        await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n        console.log('Bug updated! Final URL:', page.url());\n      }\n\n      await browser.close();\n      console.log('ALL DONE');\n      process.exit(0);\n    }\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n  }\n\n  await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(WS_DIR, 'debug_sms_fail.png'), fullPage: false });\n  console.log('Login failed');\n  await browser.close();\n  process.exit(1);\n})();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":141,"output":1791,"cacheRead":107264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109196,"cost":{"input":0.00001974,"output":0.00050148,"cacheRead":0.003003392,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003524612}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779947881758,"responseId":"15505b0b-11ff-4f44-9c7d-bca35bb0397f"}}
