{"type":"message","id":"20dedec7","parentId":"eaeece52","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:03:50.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent me the TAPD cookies directly! He must have exported them from his browser. Let me save these cookies to the cookie files and use them directly.\n\nThe cookies have:\n- `tapdsession` with expiration date `1780552985` (which is around 2026-06-04, so 7 days from now)\n- `t_u` value\n- `_t_uid` = 583593082\n- `t_cloud_login` = 18068135880\n- `_t_crop` = 61182352\n\nThis is the fully authenticated session. Let me save this to the cookie files first, then kill the waiting script, then upload the attachment to bug 1016781.\n\nWait, actually - this is from the user (叶枝君)'s browser? Or 周以天's? The cookies show `t_cloud_login = 18068135880` which is 周以天's phone number, and `_t_uid = 583593082`. Let me check - looking at the MEMORY.md: 用户ID：叶枝君=1415287364, 周以天=1166740146. So `_t_uid = 583593082` is not one of these... \n\nActually, these user IDs were for the project workspace. The `_t_uid` might be a different user ID. Looking at the `t_u` value which contains `5eba8895e4a5918dd8af...`, the domain is `.tapd.cn`.\n\nIn any case, the cookies clearly show `t_cloud_login = 18068135880` which is 周以天's phone, so these are valid cookies for 周以天's session.\n\nLet me save these cookies and use them to upload the attachment. I need to:\n1. Save the cookies to the cookie files (both tapd_cookies.json and tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json)\n2. Kill the currently running SMS script\n3. Run an upload script using the new cookies","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人直接把导出的 cookie 给我了！我存下来然后上传附件。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ndjFbM1NYckYtNCm623o7986","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(process.stdin.fd, 'utf8'));\nfs.writeFileSync('tapd_cookies.json', JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\nfs.writeFileSync('tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json', JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\nconsole.log('Saved', cookies.length, 'cookies');\nconsole.log('tapdsession:', cookies.find(c=>c.name==='tapdsession')?.value?.substring(0,20)||'not found');\n\" < \\\\.\\pipe\\stdin","timeout":5,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":30371,"output":667,"cacheRead":80256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111294,"cost":{"input":0.00425194,"output":0.00018676,"cacheRead":0.002247168,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006685868}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779948222003,"responseId":"e1c46894-b3c6-4aea-b8e3-4a53472e05b8"}}
