{"type":"message","id":"a9ea108b","parentId":"0044f44a","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:04:22.367Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Cookies saved successfully. tapdsession expires on 2026-06-04, so 7 days from today. Now I need to:\n\n1. Kill the SMS waiting script (quick-slug)\n2. Upload the video to bug 1016781 using the fresh cookies\n3. Set up the cron job for daily keepalive\n\nLet me first kill the waiting script.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Cookie 存好了，有效期到 6月4日。现在杀 SMS 脚本，用新 cookie 上传附件。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ptY2yeutfVtgsIx8coqf4684","name":"subagents","arguments":{"action":"list"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":87,"output":148,"cacheRead":114816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115051,"cost":{"input":0.00001218,"output":0.00004144,"cacheRead":0.0032148479999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0032684679999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779948259921,"responseId":"9a1eed01-aa87-4d21-8181-7644d7d4573b"}}
