{"type":"message","id":"77a362c5","parentId":"f190e7b4","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:06:19.483Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"提交成功了！Final URL 跳转到了 bug list 页面，说明表单提交成功。视频附件已经上传到 bug 1016781。\n\n现在还需要：\n1. ✅ 保存 cookie ✅\n2. ✅ 上传视频附件到 bug 1016781 ✅\n3. 设置 cron 保活任务\n\n让我清理临时文件并设置 cron。\n\n不过先等等，之前的 SMS 等待脚本（quick-slug）还在后台跑吗？让我检查一下。如果是的话需要杀掉。\n\n然后我需要给主人汇报结果，并设置保活 cron。\n\n对于 cron 的设置，OpenClaw 使用 `cron` 方式来设置定时任务。让我查一下怎么用。\n\n实际上，在 OpenClaw 中，cron 是通过 `openclaw cron` 命令或者 `gateway` 配置来管理的。让我看看 docs。\n\n其实也可以直接用 `sessions_spawn` 配合 cron 表达式。让我看看具体的用法。\n\n从 skills 来看，有 TaskFlow skill。但设置 cron 最直接的方式是用 `openclaw cron` 命令行工具。\n\n让我问问主人是否要把保活脚本设成 cron 定时任务，每天固定时间跑。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"视频已成功上传到 bug 1016781 ✅\n\n现在清理临时文件，然后设置保活 cron。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_O736K34aTlok6rVKrJ8h7376","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Remove-Item scripts\\upload_bug_attachment.mjs,scripts\\upload_bug_v2.mjs,scripts\\tapd_login_v2.mjs,scripts\\tapd_login_with_code.mjs,scripts\\tapd_login_sms.mjs,scripts\\save_cookies.mjs,scripts\\tapd_password_login.mjs,scripts\\tapd_full_login_attach.mjs,scripts\\step1_send_sms.mjs,scripts\\temp_relogin_attach.mjs,scripts\\temp_tapd_relogin.mjs,scripts\\temp_attach_v2.mjs,scripts\\temp_create_bug.mjs,tapd_qrcode.png,tapd_qrcode_v2.png,debug_login_fail.png,debug_login_page.png,debug_login_final.png,debug_sms_fail.png,tapd_login_headed.png,_sms_code.json -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\"","timeout":5,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":171,"output":552,"cacheRead":118656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119379,"cost":{"input":0.00002394,"output":0.00015456,"cacheRead":0.003322368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003500868}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779948372652,"responseId":"27864a01-f369-4476-a6c4-74019c1dbbeb"}}
