{"type":"message","id":"18bf9d75","parentId":"6ebd5683","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:06:24.645Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_gxY4CoXKMZm3dZeX9kYd1576","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.7 (eeef486) — If you can describe it, I can probably automate it—or at least make it funnier.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  show        Show a cron job\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2417,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.7 (eeef486) — If you can describe it, I can probably automate it—or at least make it funnier.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  show        Show a cron job\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779948384645}}
