{"type":"message","id":"c8aa2ed9","parentId":"3f0ca0d9","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:06:57.647Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No cron in the config yet. Let me check the full config to understand the structure better, then see if I can add a cron job section.\n\nActually, looking at the `openclaw cron add` output, it says \"scope upgrade pending approval\". The gateway has security scopes and \"cron\" scope needs to be approved by the user.\n\nLet me just tell the user about this and ask them to approve it. Or I can use a different approach.\n\nActually, the `openclaw cron add` command produced a pending approval. The user might have received a prompt. Let me just tell the user what happened and ask them to run the approval command.\n\nAlternatively, I can add the cron via the tui interface or via API call.\n\nLet me just tell the user to approve it and I'll set up the cron.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，加 cron 需要你先 approve 一下权限。你收到一个 scope 升级的提示了吗？\n\n或者我换个方式——直接把 cron 配置写进 `openclaw.json`，你重启一下网关就行？\n\n另外附件的事搞定了：\n- ✅ cookie 已保存（有效期到 6月4日）\n- ✅ 视频已上传到 bug [1016781](https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/bug/detail/1131253609001016781)\n\n现在要做的是**设一个每天跑一次的保活 cron**，你看哪种方式方便：\n1. **你 approve 权限**，我直接 `openclaw cron add` 加\n2. **我改配置文件**，你 `openclaw gateway restart` 生效\n3. **先不管**，等 cookie 快过期了我提醒你重新导出"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":120,"output":355,"cacheRead":123264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123739,"cost":{"input":0.000016800000000000002,"output":0.0000994,"cacheRead":0.0034513919999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0035675919999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779948412177,"responseId":"6e85e3c3-4f1f-4ac6-bf24-22d3d04c2b9a"}}
